# GeoJSONDelegate

**Interface**

A delegate object that controls a GeoJSON import to override default behavior and provide custom style.

## Declaration

```swift
interface GeoJSONDelegate
```

## Overview

The delegate object provides hooks into the key moments in the GeoJSON import process. When you pass a delegate object to the [doc://com.apple.mapkitjs/documentation/MapKitJS/mapkit/importGeoJSON] method, you can:

- Modify or replace annotations and overlays before MapKit JS adds them to the [doc://com.apple.mapkitjs/documentation/MapKitJS/ItemCollection] object.
- Override the default GeoJSON mapping behavior.
- Provide custom styling by implementing [doc://com.apple.mapkitjs/documentation/MapKitJS/GeoJSONDelegate/styleForOverlay].
- Receive feedback on the result from importing GeoJSON data.

## Overriding items

- **itemForFeature(item, geoJSON)**: Overrides a feature.
- **itemForFeatureCollection(itemCollection, geoJSON)**: Overrides a feature collection.
- **itemForLineString(overlay, geoJSON)**: Overrides a line string.
- **itemForMultiLineString(itemCollection, geoJSON)**: Overrides a multiline string.
- **itemForPoint(coordinate, geoJSON)**: Overrides a point.
- **itemForMultiPoint(itemCollection, geoJSON)**: Overrides a multipoint object.
- **itemForPolygon(overlay, geoJSON)**: Overrides a polygon.
- **itemForMultiPolygon(itemCollection, geoJSON)**: Overrides a multipolygon.
- **styleForOverlay(overlay, geoJSON)**: Overrides the style of overlays.

## Handling errors and completion

- **geoJSONDidComplete(result, geoJSON)**: Completes the GeoJSON import.
- **geoJSONDidError(error, geoJSON)**: Indicates when the GeoJSON import fails.

## Instance Methods

- **itemForGeometryCollection(item, object)**: Overrides a geometry collection with the provided item and object.

## Geographical features

- **importGeoJSON(data, callback)**: Converts imported GeoJSON data to MapKit JS compatible items.
- **Item**: A type alias that represents all objects that the framework sets in an item collection.
- **ItemCollection**: A tree structure containing annotations, overlays, and nested item collection objects.
- **GeoJSONImporterCallback**: A callback function that MapKit JS invokes when importing a GeoJSON object.
- **GeoJSONImportError**: An error object that indicates an error occurred while importing a GeoJSON object.
- **Displaying Indoor Maps with MapKit JS**: Use the Indoor Mapping Data Format (IMDF) to show an indoor map with custom overlays and points of interest in your browser.
